{"tid":288620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好鐘意陳柏宇？","createTime":"2017-06-18T10:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T18:14:40.000Z","uid":65974,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30570ae27738e55135b354daf3838b663a3ef6dc","tid":288620,"uid":65974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:28:42.000Z","msg":"我覺得陳柏宇唱歌好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由I Miss You開始就鐘意咗佢<br />\n好多首歌都好好聽 日日都聽<br />\n你瞞我瞞 斷絕來往 固執 逸後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到近期嘅 回眸一笑 別來無恙 告別之前<br />\nThe Players 演唱會又好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽住果首 沒有你 我什麼都不是<br />\n今年男神都結婚了<br />\n不知不覺已經成11年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好希望陳柏宇終有一日係紅館開演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴絲都同我一樣鐘意左陳柏宇咁多年？"},{"pid":"900040dd8dbaf171b8572ab6972c134f74f261c4","tid":288620,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"這份愛太神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f841264d7939bd40d7e2b5ec186a3d349588b7","tid":288620,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"3d3bd0ad0fde580ce2867be05129bccc6d7ebd92","tid":288620,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"耐過你 固執開始"},{"pid":"b988c81977180b6cac125151918e292109be0f9e","tid":288620,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7670cba4c24d6b40b39b3f4db8f909cd29685128","tid":288620,"uid":30758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:39:53.000Z","msg":"聽講年尾紅館開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f14a105d64d8df690d1